GLES record store (trap 17, ES half): RESOLVED single-source. New
build/slang_shaders.zig mechanism `gles_define` compiles a SECOND SPIR-V
leg with -DSNAIL_TARGET_GLES; the family source binds Texture2D<uint>
(R32UI, row-major, width 1024) there instead of Buffer<uint>. Both the
